THANKS
------

Ivf++ has originally been written by Jonas Lindemann. Many people further contributed to Ivf++ 
by reporting problems, suggesting various improvements or submitting actual code. Here is a 
list of these people:

Carl-Johan Lejdfors, autoconf/automake on linux system
Pierre Olsson, Testing
Rikard Larsson, Testing
Per-Anders Wernberg, Testing 
Derek Pang, Testing and feedback
Ola Dahlblom, Checking the documentation
John Aspras, TGA and BMP image reading classes (See ivfext library)

